## 一、6 个 Bounded Context（与 Service 一一对应）

| Context | Service | Aggregate Root | 核心职责 |
|---|---|---|---|
| **User Context** | `user_service` | `User` | 注册/登录/资料/隐私 |
| **Diagnosis Context** | `diagnosis_service` | `Diagnosis` | 上传/分析/报告生成 |
| **Plan Context** | `plan_service` | `TodayPlan` | 21 天计划/任务/打卡 |
| **Community Context** | `community_service` | `Post` | 帖子/评论/点赞 |
| **Video Context** | `video_service` | `Video` | 视频搜索/播放/降级 |
| **Notification Context** | `notification_service` | `Notification` | 推送/站内信/邮件 |

