## 二、Context 间通信：Domain Event 驱动

### 禁止项

| 禁止 | 正确做法 |
|---------|------------|
| Context A 直接 import Context B 的 Service/Model | 发布 Domain Event |
| Context A 直接查询 Context B 的数据库表 | 订阅 Domain Event + 本地只读副本 |
| 在 API 层手动调用多个 Service 后拼装响应 | 各 Context 独立响应，通过 EventBus 协调 |

### Domain Event 命名规范

```
<Aggregate><Action>Event
```

**正例**：`UserRegisteredEvent`、`DiagnosisCompletedEvent`、`CheckinSubmittedEvent`、`PlanActivatedEvent`

**反例**：`user_event`、`onDiagnosis`、`send_notification`

### 12 个核心 Domain Event

| Event | Producer | Consumer | 触发时机 |
|---|---|---|---|
| `UserRegisteredEvent` | User | Notification, Community | 用户注册成功 |
| `DiagnosisCompletedEvent` | Diagnosis | Plan, Notification | 诊断报告生成 |
| `DiagnosisFailedEvent` | Diagnosis | Notification | 诊断失败（含降级） |
| `PlanActivatedEvent` | Plan | Notification | 21 天计划激活 |
| `TaskAssignedEvent` | Plan | Notification, Community | 新任务分配 |
| `CheckinSubmittedEvent` | Plan | Community, Notification | 用户打卡 |
| `PostCreatedEvent` | Community | Notification, Safety | 发布帖子 |
| `PostModeratedEvent` | Community | Notification | 审核完成 |
| `VideoSearchedEvent` | Video | Analytics | 视频搜索 |
| `NotificationSentEvent` | Notification | Analytics | 推送已发送 |
| `UserDeactivatedEvent` | User | 全部 | 用户注销 |
| `ConsentGrantedEvent` | User | 全部 | 用户授权 |

