## 六、自审命令

```bash
# L4：跨 Context 直接导入检测
grep -rn "from app.contexts.user" backend/app/contexts/diagnosis/ && echo "FAIL" || echo "PASS"

# L4：Domain Event 命名规范
grep -rn 'Event\s*=' backend/app/contexts/ | grep -v 'Event\s*=\s*"[A-Z][a-zA-Z]*Event"' && echo "FAIL" || echo "PASS"

# L4：禁止跨 Context 共享数据库表
grep -rn "from app.contexts.user.infrastructure" backend/app/contexts/diagnosis/ && echo "FAIL" || echo "PASS"

# L4：禁止在新 Context 中使用 services/
grep -rn "from app.services" backend/app/contexts/ && echo "FAIL" || echo "PASS"
```

